---
title: Garlicky Dijon Chicken Risotto with Veggies & Double Parmesan
description: How much do we love risotto? We love risotto so much that we’ve prepared a special one for you tonight. Leek, celery and corn make up the base of this dish, with bites of chicken throughout. Dijon mustard flavours this baked rice dish to give it an extra kick.
